channel.title: Wont even let me log on!HELP
channel.description:
OK so i get all these error messages saying no responce from server, server is offline blah blah blah.
i double checked everything that you can possibly check
my java is jdk 20 and the run server says this when i hit edit
[code]@echo off @title Server cd Server java -Xmx512m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.20-ga-bin.jar server[/code]
heres some pics that i made when i double check everything
[IMG]http://img535.imageshack.us/img535/6601/duct.jpg[/img] the server is running
[IMG]http://img692.imageshack.us/img692/1167/sucess.jpg[/img] i portforwarded correctly this is showing my ports are open
[IMG]http://img686.imageshack.us/img686/4329/192zx.jpg[/img]
this is my router showing that i have my server checked off
[IMG]http://img155.imageshack.us/img155/6285/noerrors.jpg[/img] the server is offline thing, even though my server has 0 errors and i compiled,and i get no compiling errors either!
i took the time to post all these pics can some1 just try to see whats wrong i've tried so many servers and none let me on.
